sub_title: MSc Accounting & Financial Management student at Erasmus University Rotterdam
summary:
Young and ambitious student currently pursuing my Master in Accounting & Financial Management at the Erasmus University of Rotterdam. 

I have vast experience in the hospitality business as I have worked part-time alongside my studies for 5 years. In this time my main skills obtained include time management, communication, teamwork and the ability to work hard under stressful circumstances.
